    <title>Web-文件上传漏洞</title>
    <link href="undefined2019/11/10/2/"/>
    <url>2019/11/10/2/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Web-文件上传漏洞"><a href="#Web-文件上传漏洞" class="headerlink" title="Web-文件上传漏洞"></a>Web-文件上传漏洞</h2><h3 id="漏洞描述："><a href="#漏洞描述：" class="headerlink" title="漏洞描述："></a>漏洞描述：</h3><p>Web应用程序通常会有文件上传的功能，比如：我们上传自己的头像，在招聘网站上传自己附件简历，只有Web程序允许上传文件就有可能存在文件上传漏洞，有些网站存在文件上传功能，但是对上传的文件没有进行验证，从而形成文件上传漏洞，另一种情况就是对上传的文件检验不严格，上传者可以进行绕过，形成文件上传漏洞。</p><h3 id="漏洞危害："><a href="#漏洞危害：" class="headerlink" title="漏洞危害："></a>漏洞危害：</h3><p>文件上传漏洞与SQL注入相比，其危害更大，如果Web应用程序存在文件上传漏洞，我们可以直接上传WebShell到服务器上面，大部分情况下，我们是上传一句话木马，然后利用菜刀或者蚁剑进行连接，然后再进行提权等操作，所以说文件上传漏洞的危害非常大。</p><p>文件上传漏洞一般是配合解析漏洞一起利用，我们这里主要利用一些CTF比赛的题目来进行进一步了解，Upload-labs是一个帮你总结所有类型的上传漏洞的靶场，包括常见的文件上传漏洞，我们会在这十九关中挑选几关来为大家讲解。</p><h4 id="第二关"><a href="#第二关" class="headerlink" title="第二关"></a>第二关</h4><p>我们可以先看一下源代码：</p><p>真实环境中通过哪种方式能绕过上传限制完全是靠自己的经验和多多尝试。</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$is_upload = <span class="keyword">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">$msg = <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">isset</span>($_POST[<span class="string">'submit'</span>])) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (file_exists(UPLOAD_PATH)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (($_FILES[<span class="string">'upload_file'</span>][<span class="string">'type'</span>] == <span class="string">'image/jpeg'</span>) || ($_FILES[<span class="string">'upload_file'</span>][<span class="string">'type'</span>] == <span class="string">'image/png'</span>) || ($_FILES[<span class="string">'upload_file'</span>][<span class="string">'type'</span>] == <span class="string">'image/gif'</span>)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            $temp_file = $_FILES[<span class="string">'upload_file'</span>][<span class="string">'tmp_name'</span>];</span><br><span class="line">            $img_path = UPLOAD_PATH . <span class="string">'/'</span> . $_FILES[<span class="string">'upload_file'</span>][<span class="string">'name'</span>]            </span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (move_uploaded_file($temp_file, $img_path)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                $is_upload = <span class="keyword">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                $msg = <span class="string">'上传出错！'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            $msg = <span class="string">'文件类型不正确，请重新上传！'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        $msg = UPLOAD_PATH.<span class="string">'文件夹不存在,请手工创建！'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>发现仅仅是对content-type做了判断，我们可以通过burpsuite修改content-type绕过：</p><img src="/2019/11/10/2/1.jpg" srcset="/img/loading.gif" class=""><p>然后我们拿到上传后的URL，添加到蚁剑进行连接</p><img src="/2019/11/10/2/2.jpg" srcset="/img/loading.gif" class=""><p>我们可以看到已经连接成功</p><img src="/2019/11/10/2/3.jpg" srcset="/img/loading.gif" class=""><p>因为是CTF的题目，所以我们拿到Flag就成功了</p><img src="/2019/11/10/2/4.jpg" srcset="/img/loading.gif" class=""><h4 id="第三关"><a href="#第三关" class="headerlink" title="第三关"></a>第三关</h4><p>首先我们看一下源代码：</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$is_upload = <span class="keyword">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">$msg = <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">isset</span>($_POST[<span class="string">'submit'</span>])) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (file_exists(UPLOAD_PATH)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        $deny_ext = <span class="keyword">array</span>(<span class="string">'.asp'</span>,<span class="string">'.aspx'</span>,<span class="string">'.php'</span>,<span class="string">'.jsp'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        $file_name = trim($_FILES[<span class="string">'upload_file'</span>][<span class="string">'name'</span>]);</span><br><span class="line">        $file_name = deldot($file_name);<span class="comment">//删除文件名末尾的点</span></span><br><span class="line">        $file_ext = strrchr($file_name, <span class="string">'.'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        $file_ext = strtolower($file_ext); <span class="comment">//转换为小写</span></span><br><span class="line">        $file_ext = str_ireplace(<span class="string">'::$DATA'</span>, <span class="string">''</span>, $file_ext);<span class="comment">//去除字符串::$DATA</span></span><br><span class="line">        $file_ext = trim($file_ext); <span class="comment">//收尾去空</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(!in_array($file_ext, $deny_ext)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            $temp_file = $_FILES[<span class="string">'upload_file'</span>][<span class="string">'tmp_name'</span>];</span><br><span class="line">            $img_path = UPLOAD_PATH.<span class="string">'/'</span>.date(<span class="string">"YmdHis"</span>).rand(<span class="number">1000</span>,<span class="number">9999</span>).$file_ext;            </span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (move_uploaded_file($temp_file,$img_path)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                 $is_upload = <span class="keyword">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                $msg = <span class="string">'上传出错！'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            $msg = <span class="string">'不允许上传.asp,.aspx,.php,.jsp后缀文件！'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        $msg = UPLOAD_PATH . <span class="string">'文件夹不存在,请手工创建！'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我们发现进行了黑名单验证，禁止了后缀是asp、aspx、php、jsp文件上传，可以使用phtml、php3进行绕过，因为他们也是会以php运行文件</p><p>我们还是用burpsuite进行改包</p><img src="/2019/11/10/2/6.png" srcset="/img/loading.gif" class=""><p>之后的步骤就跟第二关一样了，用蚁剑进行连接</p><img src="/2019/11/10/2/7.png" srcset="/img/loading.gif" class=""><p>然后打开虚拟终端查看Flag</p><img src="/2019/11/10/2/4.jpg" srcset="/img/loading.gif" class=""><p>因为这些题目都是来自同一个CTF平台，所以Flag是一样的</p><h4 id="第四关"><a href="#第四关" class="headerlink" title="第四关"></a>第四关</h4><p>同样是查看源代码：</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$is_upload = <span class="keyword">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">$msg = <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">isset</span>($_POST[<span class="string">'submit'</span>])) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (file_exists(UPLOAD_PATH)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        $deny_ext = <span class="keyword">array</span>(<span class="string">".php"</span>,<span class="string">".php5"</span>,<span class="string">".php4"</span>,<span class="string">".php3"</span>,<span class="string">".php2"</span>,<span class="string">"php1"</span>,<span class="string">".html"</span>,<span class="string">".htm"</span>,<span class="string">".phtml"</span>,<span class="string">".pht"</span>,<span class="string">".pHp"</span>,<span class="string">".pHp5"</span>,<span class="string">".pHp4"</span>,<span class="string">".pHp3"</span>,<span class="string">".pHp2"</span>,<span class="string">"pHp1"</span>,<span class="string">".Html"</span>,<span class="string">".Htm"</span>,<span class="string">".pHtml"</span>,<span class="string">".jsp"</span>,<span class="string">".jspa"</span>,<span class="string">".jspx"</span>,<span class="string">".jsw"</span>,<span class="string">".jsv"</span>,<span class="string">".jspf"</span>,<span class="string">".jtml"</span>,<span class="string">".jSp"</span>,<span class="string">".jSpx"</span>,<span class="string">".jSpa"</span>,<span class="string">".jSw"</span>,<span class="string">".jSv"</span>,<span class="string">".jSpf"</span>,<span class="string">".jHtml"</span>,<span class="string">".asp"</span>,<span class="string">".aspx"</span>,<span class="string">".asa"</span>,<span class="string">".asax"</span>,<span class="string">".ascx"</span>,<span class="string">".ashx"</span>,<span class="string">".asmx"</span>,<span class="string">".cer"</span>,<span class="string">".aSp"</span>,<span class="string">".aSpx"</span>,<span class="string">".aSa"</span>,<span class="string">".aSax"</span>,<span class="string">".aScx"</span>,<span class="string">".aShx"</span>,<span class="string">".aSmx"</span>,<span class="string">".cEr"</span>,<span class="string">".sWf"</span>,<span class="string">".swf"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        $file_name = trim($_FILES[<span class="string">'upload_file'</span>][<span class="string">'name'</span>]);</span><br><span class="line">        $file_name = deldot($file_name);<span class="comment">//删除文件名末尾的点</span></span><br><span class="line">        $file_ext = strrchr($file_name, <span class="string">'.'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        $file_ext = strtolower($file_ext); <span class="comment">//转换为小写</span></span><br><span class="line">        $file_ext = str_ireplace(<span class="string">'::$DATA'</span>, <span class="string">''</span>, $file_ext);<span class="comment">//去除字符串::$DATA</span></span><br><span class="line">        $file_ext = trim($file_ext); <span class="comment">//收尾去空</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (!in_array($file_ext, $deny_ext)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            $temp_file = $_FILES[<span class="string">'upload_file'</span>][<span class="string">'tmp_name'</span>];</span><br><span class="line">            $img_path = UPLOAD_PATH.<span class="string">'/'</span>.$file_name;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (move_uploaded_file($temp_file, $img_path)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                $is_upload = <span class="keyword">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                $msg = <span class="string">'上传出错！'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            $msg = <span class="string">'此文件不允许上传!'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        $msg = UPLOAD_PATH . <span class="string">'文件夹不存在,请手工创建！'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>也是采用的是黑名单过滤，几乎过滤了所有的危险的后缀名，但是没有过滤.htaccess,我们可以利用它突破限制，这里也可以使用.user.ini，原理相似。</p><p>首先上传一个.htaccess文件，文件内容是：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">AddType application/x-httpd-php .jpg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>所有以jpg结尾的文件都会PHP解析</p><p>然后我们再上传一个包含一句话木马的图片，注意要以jpg结尾</p><img src="/2019/11/10/2/9.png" srcset="/img/loading.gif" class=""><p>同样蚁剑添加数据连接</p><img src="/2019/11/10/2/10.png" srcset="/img/loading.gif" class=""><p>然后打开虚拟终端查看Flag</p><img src="/2019/11/10/2/4.jpg" srcset="/img/loading.gif" class=""><h4 id="第六关"><a href="#第六关" class="headerlink" title="第六关"></a>第六关</h4><p>查看源码：</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$is_upload = <span class="keyword">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">$msg = <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">isset</span>($_POST[<span class="string">'submit'</span>])) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (file_exists(UPLOAD_PATH)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        $deny_ext = <span class="keyword">array</span>(<span class="string">".php"</span>,<span class="string">".php5"</span>,<span class="string">".php4"</span>,<span class="string">".php3"</span>,<span class="string">".php2"</span>,<span class="string">".html"</span>,<span class="string">".htm"</span>,<span class="string">".phtml"</span>,<span class="string">".pht"</span>,<span class="string">".pHp"</span>,<span class="string">".pHp5"</span>,<span class="string">".pHp4"</span>,<span class="string">".pHp3"</span>,<span class="string">".pHp2"</span>,<span class="string">".Html"</span>,<span class="string">".Htm"</span>,<span class="string">".pHtml"</span>,<span class="string">".jsp"</span>,<span class="string">".jspa"</span>,<span class="string">".jspx"</span>,<span class="string">".jsw"</span>,<span class="string">".jsv"</span>,<span class="string">".jspf"</span>,<span class="string">".jtml"</span>,<span class="string">".jSp"</span>,<span class="string">".jSpx"</span>,<span class="string">".jSpa"</span>,<span class="string">".jSw"</span>,<span class="string">".jSv"</span>,<span class="string">".jSpf"</span>,<span class="string">".jHtml"</span>,<span class="string">".asp"</span>,<span class="string">".aspx"</span>,<span class="string">".asa"</span>,<span class="string">".asax"</span>,<span class="string">".ascx"</span>,<span class="string">".ashx"</span>,<span class="string">".asmx"</span>,<span class="string">".cer"</span>,<span class="string">".aSp"</span>,<span class="string">".aSpx"</span>,<span class="string">".aSa"</span>,<span class="string">".aSax"</span>,<span class="string">".aScx"</span>,<span class="string">".aShx"</span>,<span class="string">".aSmx"</span>,<span class="string">".cEr"</span>,<span class="string">".sWf"</span>,<span class="string">".swf"</span>,<span class="string">".htaccess"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        $file_name = $_FILES[<span class="string">'upload_file'</span>][<span class="string">'name'</span>];</span><br><span class="line">        $file_name = deldot($file_name);<span class="comment">//删除文件名末尾的点</span></span><br><span class="line">        $file_ext = strrchr($file_name, <span class="string">'.'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        $file_ext = strtolower($file_ext); <span class="comment">//转换为小写</span></span><br><span class="line">        $file_ext = str_ireplace(<span class="string">'::$DATA'</span>, <span class="string">''</span>, $file_ext);<span class="comment">//去除字符串::$DATA</span></span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (!in_array($file_ext, $deny_ext)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            $temp_file = $_FILES[<span class="string">'upload_file'</span>][<span class="string">'tmp_name'</span>];</span><br><span class="line">            $img_path = UPLOAD_PATH.<span class="string">'/'</span>.date(<span class="string">"YmdHis"</span>).rand(<span class="number">1000</span>,<span class="number">9999</span>).$file_ext;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (move_uploaded_file($temp_file,$img_path)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                $is_upload = <span class="keyword">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                $msg = <span class="string">'上传出错！'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            $msg = <span class="string">'此文件不允许上传'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        $msg = UPLOAD_PATH . <span class="string">'文件夹不存在,请手工创建！'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>还是黑名单过滤，但是没有对文件后缀进行去空格处理，可以加空格进行绕过</p><img src="/2019/11/10/2/11.png" srcset="/img/loading.gif" class=""><p>蚁剑添加数据连接</p><img src="/2019/11/10/2/12.png" srcset="/img/loading.gif" class=""><p>虚拟终端查看Flag</p><img src="/2019/11/10/2/4.jpg" srcset="/img/loading.gif" class=""><h3 id="修补建议："><a href="#修补建议：" class="headerlink" title="修补建议："></a>修补建议：</h3><p>建立白名单过滤，白名单会比黑名单相对更安全</p><p>对于存放上传文件的目录，限定目录的权限（不要给执行权限）</p><p>对文件进行重命名</p><hr><p>到这里我们就介绍完了</p><p>其实文件上传还有很多姿势，这里就不一一列举了，有兴趣的同学可以自己研究研究</p><p>此次用到的CTF平台<a href="https://buuoj.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BUUCTF 训练平台</a></p><p>这里是关于<a href="https://xz.aliyun.com/t/2435" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Upload-labs通关手册</a>,建议先自己独立思考。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
